message:
Just FYI - The Google Cloud team just pushed out a full codelab on #Dataflow and a half-day codelab on #Tensorflow, as well as a 3h University session on Tensorflow.

Dataflow codelab
https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/cloud-dataflow-nyc-taxi-tycoon

Tensorflow codelab
https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/cloud-tensorflow-mnist

Dataflow blog post
https://cloud.google.com/blog/big-data/2017/01/learn-real-time-processing-with-a-new-public-data-stream-and-google-cloud-dataflow-codelab

Tensorflow blog post
https://cloud.google.com/blog/big-data/2017/01/learn-tensorflow-and-deep-learning-without-a-phd

Tensorflow 3h video for machine learning beginners
https://youtu.be/vq2nnJ4g6N0

Tensorflow 1h video for machine learning beginners
